Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.78,0:22:23.22,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}様々なネガティブに{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:28.73,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}とらわれるほど弱くはない{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.83,0:22:33.27,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(230,230)\blur20}{\i0}孤独も知らぬTrickster{\i}
